title: Anne of Green Gables
creator: Lucy Maud Montgomery
description: LibriVox recording of Anne of Green Gables. For more information about our readers, see: http://librivox.org/anne-of-green-gables-version-5-by-lucy-maud-montgomery. Anne of Green Gables is about an orphan girl who is starving for a family to love her. Her big words and bright spirits take her through many toils, trials, and temptations. Her romantic schemes make it nearly to impossible for any day of her life to be ordinary. Anne Shirley who was once a poor orphan girl learns through the care of Marilla and Matthew Cuthbert, to live, love, and learn. (Summary by Robinsgirl) M4B format available
